quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  47,1,"Wֽ»n a wֽ»po nokorװ‘ no na wֽ»si (amanfoֽ») kwan firi Nyankopֽ»n kwan no soֽ» no, (Onyankopֽ»n) b־µma wֽ»nwuma ay־µ kwa."
  47,2,"Wֽ»n nso a wֽ»agye adie na wֽ»di dwuma pa, na wֽ»gye de־µ yֹ›asane ama Muhammad no die s־µ ־µno ne nokor־µ a efiri wֽ»n Wura Nyankopֽ»n hֽ» no, ֶ†b־µpepa wֽ»n bֽ»ne afiri wֽ»n so na Way־µ wֽ»n abrabֽ» mu yie (ama wֽ»n)."
  47,3,"Efris־µ, wֽ»n a wֽ»po nokorװ‘ no di nkontompo akyi, ־µna wֽ»n a wֽ»agye adie no nso di nokor־µ a efiri wֽ»n Wura Nyankopֽ»n hֽ» no akyi. Saa na Nyankopֽ»n de wֽ»n y־µ mfatoho ma adasamma."
  47,4,"Enti s־µ mo ne aboniay־µfoֽ» no hyia wֽ» ֽ»koo mu a, montwitwa wֽ»n kֽ»n nkosi s־µ mobֹ›di wֽ»n so nkonim, na monfa wֽ»n nnomum, na mongu wֽ»n mpokyer־µ mmia mu; na akyire yi a ֽ»koo no aguo no, (mobֹ›tumi} adom (de wֽ»n ho aky־µ wֽ»n), anaas־µ (mobֹ›tumi) ama wֽ»n atua mpata. Saa ara na s־µ Nyankopֽ»n p־µ a, nka ֶ†no ara b־µtwe wֽ»n aso, na mmom s־µde־µ ֶ†de mo ho b־µy־µ mo ho mo ho nsֽ»hw־µ. Wֽ»n a yֹ›aku wֽ»n wֽ» Nyankopֽ»n kwan soֽ» no nso ֶ†mma wֽ»n nnwuma nny־µ kwa."
  47,5,"ֶ†b־µtene wֽ»n na Way־µ wֽ»n asetena mu yie,"
  47,6,"Na ֶ†de wֽ»n awura Soro aheman no a ֶ†de akyer־µ wֽ»n no mu."
  47,7,"Mo a moagye adie, s־µ moboa Nyankopֽ»n a ֶ†no nso b־µboa mo, na Wama moagyina moanan so pintin."
  47,8,"Na wֽ»n a wֽ»nnye nnie no de־µ, ֽ»s־µe־µ na ־µwֽ» wֽ»n soֽ», na (Nyankopֽ»n) b־µma wֽ»n nnwuma ay־µ kwa."
  47,9,"Efiris־µ wֽ»mp־µ ade־µ a Nyankopֽ»n asane aba no, enti Wama wֽ»n nnwuma (nyinaa) ay־µ kwa."
  47,10,"Enti wֽ»ntu kwan wֽ» asaase no so nhw־µ s־µde־µ boniay־µfoֽ» no a wֽ»dii kan no awiee־µ si wiee־µ? Onyankopֽ»n s־µee wֽ»n pasaa. Na boniay־µfoֽ» no wֽ» ne (saa asotwee no) s־µ so."
  47,11,"Efiris־µ Nyankopֽ»n ne wֽ»n a wֽ»agye adie no Kyitaafoֽ», na boniay־µfoֽ» no de־µ wֽ»nni okyitaafoֽ» biara."